Interface CollectionDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
MockCollectionDAO
public interface CollectionDAOInterface
The CollectionDAOInterface defines the contract for data access operations related to Collection objects. It specifies methods for inserting new collections, retrieving all collections, retrieving collections by user, and getting the collection ID by user and collection name.
